data.title: President’s List at Peru State College – Spring Term 2024
data.text:
Spring 2024 President's List Recipients

(Peru, Nebraska) Peru State College has published the President's List for the Spring Term 2024. The list includes students from Nebraska, 17 other states, Puerto Rico, and students from countries including the Dominican Republic, the United Kingdom, and Venezuela. To qualify for the President’s List, students must maintain a grade point average of 4.0 for the semester, complete at least 12 graded credit hours, have no incomplete grades, and be degree-seeking.

If you have any questions, contact the Student Records Office for further information at 402-872-2276.
